  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
  normal"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
  font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;
  mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:
  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Related variables<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  </td>
  <td width="504" valign="top" style="width: 5.25in; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: black; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: black; padding: 0in 5.4pt;">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
  normal"><span style="mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:
  Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  color:#010101">MAX_SOCKETSET_THREADS, </span><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:
  10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  color:#010101"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
  normal"><span style="mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:
  Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  color:#010101">MAX_CONNECTIONS</span><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
  mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  color:#010101"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style="font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">Short Description</b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">In order to serve multiple connections, internally Xpl
module creates a connection pool. Internally the connection pool is implemented
using a socket set and this socket set is served by a set of thread. The
variable SOCKETS_PER_SOCKETSET specifies the maximum number of sockets per
socket set. <o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Long Description</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;By default the socket
sets contains 60 sockets and 6 threads serves them. In large environments with
more connections, keeping the socket set smaller is more efficient. <o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">For example in an environment with the default socket set ie
60 and served by 6 threads(1:10), even if&nbsp;
59 connections are closed whole socket set is active in the memory.&nbsp; In such scenarios if the number of threads is
3 and the socket set is 10(1:3), the number of threads are thrice the number
sockets; as result requests gets processed faster and a faster release of the
socket set. Due to this very reason in large environments where the number of
connections are very high keeping the value of SOCKETS_PER_SOCKETSET to 10
and&nbsp; MAX_SOCKETSET_THREADS to 3 makes is
recommended.<span style="font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">&nbsp;</span></p><h2 style="margin: 0.25in 0in 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><a name="_Toc491176822"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: rgb(46, 116, 181); font-weight: normal;">MAX_SOCKETSET_THREADS</span></span></a><span class="LabelChar"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size:13.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:
major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;
color:#2E74B5;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2><table class="MsoTableGrid" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="0" style="border-left: none;">
