  windows platform)</span><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:
  Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;
  mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#2E74B5;mso-themecolor:accent1;
