</tbody></table><span style="font-size: medium; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;"><b>Short Description</b></span><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3">HPE Operation Agents HTTPS communication is based on the
TCP/IP protocol, the industry standard for reliable networking. Using the
Secure Socket Layer (SSL) protocol, HTTPS communication uses authentication to
validate who has access to data, and encryption to secure data exchange.<span style="letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">&nbsp;B</span></font><span style="font-size: medium; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">ased on the architecture the BBC module takes care about
the transmission of data between a Server and Client and vice versa. The
SSL_HANDSHAKE_TIMEOUT represents the timeout within which the SSL connection
needs to be initialized.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><b>Long Description</b><o:p></o:p></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: rgb(46, 116, 181);"><o:p><font size="3">















</font></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3">Specifies the number of seconds the BBC HttpServer will
block waiting for an SSL connection to initialize. If this timeout is exceeded
the request will be aborted. ; Default is 10 seconds.</font><o:p></o:p></p><h2 style="margin: 0.25in 0in 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font size="4" style="font-weight: normal;"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size:
13.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;
mso-ascii-theme-font:major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;
mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;color:#2E74B5;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:
191">HOSTNAME_CACHE_TIMEOUT</span></span><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: rgb(46, 116, 181);">&nbsp;</span></span></font></h2><table class="MsoTableGrid" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="0" style="border-left: none;">
