  <p class="Label"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; color: windowtext;">LCore 11.0x</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(46, 116, 181);"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
