  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
  normal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Gadugi&quot;,sans-serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
  color:#010101">SERVER_PORT<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><b><span class="LabelChar" style=""><span style="line-height: 107%; color: rgb(46, 116, 181);"><o:p style="">&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style="color: windowtext; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">Short Description</span></b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: windowtext;"><font size="3">This variable is used to define/configure
server IP address value for an HTTP communication done using BBC API.<o:p></o:p></font></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: windowtext;"><font size="3"><b>Long Description</b><o:p></o:p></font></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: windowtext;"><font size="3">The Bind address for the server port to
listen/wait for requests.<o:p></o:p></font></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: windowtext;"><font size="3">













</font></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: windowtext;"><font size="3">The socket can bind to the hostname or IP
address in either IPV6 or IPv4 network. For example, consider an OA setup which
is multi-homed. This means the system can have multiple IP addresses. ovbbccb
is the communication broker that receives messages and it forwards the message
to registered clients. Let us suppose the system has 3 IPs.&nbsp; In this case , if ovbbccb needs to explicitly
set the bind address to a specific IP out of the 3 IPs of the system, SERVER_BIND_ADDRESS
can be configured with this specific IP. This would make sure that all the
incoming traffic to ovbbccb would use the specified IP.&nbsp; &nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 13pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p><h2 style="margin: 0.25in 0in 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><a name="_Toc491176836"><span class="LabelChar"><span style="line-height: 107%; color: rgb(46, 116, 181); font-weight: normal;">CLIENT_PORT</span></span></a><span class="LabelChar"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size:13.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:107%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:
major-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-theme-font:
major-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-latin;
mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:major-bidi;
color:#2E74B5;mso-themecolor:accent1;mso-themeshade:191"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></h2><table class="MsoTableGrid" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="0" style="border-left: none;">
 <tbody><tr>
  <td width="230" valign="top" style="width: 172.25pt; border-width: 1pt; border-left-style: solid; border-color: black; border-image: initial; padding: 0in 5.4pt;">
  <p class="Label"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Gadugi&quot;,sans-serif"><b>Type</b></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Gadugi&quot;,sans-serif;color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="504" valign="top" style="width: 5.25in; border-top-width: 1pt; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-top-color: black; border-right-color: black; border-bottom-color: black; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt;">
  <p class="Label"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Gadugi, sans-serif;">Integer</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Gadugi, sans-serif; color: black;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width="230" valign="top" style="width: 172.25pt; border-right-width: 1pt; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-left: 1pt solid black; border-right-color: black; border-bottom-color: black; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt;">
  <p class="Label"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Gadugi&quot;,sans-serif"><b>Default
  Value</b><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="504" valign="top" style="width: 5.25in; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: black; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: black; padding: 0in 5.4pt;">
  <p class="Label"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Gadugi, sans-serif;">0</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Gadugi, sans-serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
